  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 14th level, your master of Hemomantic ninjutsu is nearing its peak.</p><p>When you cast a ninjutsu that deals acid, necrotic, or poison damage that is benefitting from your Refined Ninjutsu class feature and targets only 1 creature, you can double the cost of the jutsu to instead target a number of creatures equal to the number of Blood Vials you currently have.</p><p>The jutsu cast in this way cannot have its cost reduced as a result of your Chakra Recovery class feature.</p>",
